title: Gène Hanssen
text:
Gène Hanssen (born 9 January 1959) is a former <a href="Netherlands">Dutch</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Hanssen spent most of his playing career with <a href="Eredivisie">Eredivisie</a> club <a href="Roda%20JC">Roda JC</a>. At the end of his career, he had a brief spell with <a href="Tokyo%20Verdy">Verdy Kawasaki</a>, but he left the club during its first season in the <a href="J1%20League">J1 League</a>, the club agreeing to cancel his contract in July 1993.
